column4: NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "720987DB4280B0134397C0A7C93E676C", "Tribes fell apart losing memories and becoming wild.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "8757ABF94EBDE04874F6BCBDAB251D02", "I don\'t know how long I can stay sane.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "80133282406A5E934739A58C4EE64F61", "We can\'t leave it like this! They must realize the danger!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "5F077E6D42783E6E6A6C91A9D445B4DC", "Stop! Do you want to ruin the island?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "3D261A8F42A3586D7CFE6EBF3574741D", "Who are you? Move out of my way! This is the only way!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "5D909F734635AA5F345D9C96554D4C6E", "Are you telling me there\'s another way?")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "1C44E0054185D9D105C33B92B8852F0B", "If the island is ruined, it defeats the purpose! Listen to me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "C084E4F2407B78D136E54099C5B98F0C", "We\'re building a city for the island by gathering all Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "1274F18C4564605C885273A916CBBD03", "I heard that we can save the island from this danger by uniting Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "7A0D720246E5663B6EB3938DF0865B58", "I think you are right, but gathering all the Digimon, that\'s a big...")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "E455CC0D456897E0452B06965AEF4D0A", "We\'re working on it right now. Nothing is impossible!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "333CE18943737E9BD008DA997FA6ACEC", "That\'s a big job! But I\'m moved... Maybe, you guys can do it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "7CBBF8D542B9A743732477BED21BEB54", "If you believe in us, I want you to come to the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E73A59C94BB8500C3289A8AFFF0DB900]", "E93DF07D49963D3818B99FAB2FF62BA6", "Alright. I\'ll go to the city. I guess that\'s my new path!")
